Package wogwt.translatable.utils

Class Summary
DateUtils WOGWT: copied from gwt-restlet to be used to parse and format JSON dates in the format(s) required by ERRouteRequestHandler.
DOMUtils DOM utility functions for use when programmatically constructing a UI.
MathUtils Utility class for math operations
ObjectUtils Utility class for general Object operations.
ParameterizedHistoryEntryPoint Base class for entry points that adds support for using history tokens with the same format as url query parameters, like #name=john&color=blue
StringUtils Utility class for String (client)
UrlParametersFormat A formatter for url query parameters like: "key1=value1&key2=value2" Can be used with the history token (#) or with query parameters (?) See ParameterizedHistoryEntryPoint.
